casebody.data:
No. 105,

Orig.

Kansas v. Colorado. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 506 U. S. 805.]

Motion of the Special Master for award of interim fees and reimbursement of expenses for the period June 22, 1992, through February 28, 1993, granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $153,042.26 to be paid as follows: 40% by Kansas, 40% by Colorado, and 20% by the United States.
